msgid "Data Compression and Archiving"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The modules described in this chapter support data compression with the "
"zlib, gzip, bzip2, lzma, and zstd algorithms, and the creation of ZIP- and "
"tar-format archives.  See also :ref:`archiving-operations` provided by the :"
"mod:`shutil` module."
